item.title: George Harrison - Between the Devil and the Deep Blue Sea - Baritone Ukulele - Key of F, A - ukeplayalongs
item.description: Play along video for the song Between the Devil and the Deep Blue Sea by George Harrison from the channel ukeplayalongs. Chords used in the song: A, Am, A♭m, B, C, Cm, C♯dim, C♯m, D7, Daug, Em, Em7, E♭7, F, F♯7, G, G7.
